
In web.xml the context parameter 'access.impl' must be a class implementing
the access api.

The default is the solr implementation which requires the system property
'solr.solr.home' to be set to the url of a solr server or a local path to
a solr installation.

In web.xml, the context parameter 'datastream.url' must be set to the public
base url of the datastream servlet. That url will be used to construct
File entity source attributes by appending the entity id.
